main.name: Muhammad Iksan
main.bio: Hello! My name is Iksan, and I'm a programmer with a strong, dual-platform background spanning both web development and mobile applications. I don't just stick with what I know; what truly excites me is the pursuit of knowledge. I'm relentlessly focused on learning new technologies and constantly dedicated to improving my skills so I can stay sharp and bring the best, most current solutions to every project I take on.
